either has to fight in the war or stay with your
friend. Sounds like an ole tamatum to me." He turned
to the new fem bot. "I dont have a lot of time here. I
dont mean to rush you but there is an important
meeting about to take place at the destron
base....would like to come and at least see what we
are about." He turned to the other. "How about you?"
